songs.title: I Got a Little Something for You (Live in Seattle)
songs.album: Songs in A Minor (10th Anniversary Edition) [Collector’s Edition]
songs.lyrics:
Hmm, mmm, yeah, yeah
Let me tell y'all

See, now yesterday I was feeling down
When I came to Seattle
And y'all turned me around

I said, oh, Seattle, do you know what you do?
Hey, yeah, ever all that you've done for me
I got a little something for you

If you want to hear
What I gotta say, say, yeah
(Yeah)
Yeah, say yeah
(Yeah)
One more time, say yeah
(Yeah)

Oh, it's for all that you done for me
I got a little something for you
Yeah, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey
Ahh ha
